metadata.name: Water of Victory 010
metadata.description:
Trilogy Goddess Collection - WoV010
Cask of Class, Victory in every Glass.

Own a bottle of history, limited in time and supply.
Super rare hand-filled Macallan with only 339 ever bottled. 

Part 1 of a trilogy collection, all hand painted, hand filled and wax bottles. Each label is tie up to a physical bottle of whisky.

Create by the Aristocrate for the Aristocratic.

Collect the entire Trilogy collection to get a limited edition painting and 3 bottles of whiskies. 
Shipped worldwide.

Bottle comes with box, signed and numbered.
